public class ProfileType
extends TextType

Marks the vCard as being an vCard.

Code sample 

 VCard vcard = new VCard();
 ProfileType profile = new ProfileType();
 vcard.setProfile(profile);

Property name: PROFILE

Supported versions: 3.0
